    <string name="btn_volver">Back</string>
    <string name="about_body">
        🐀 Alcantarilla Trips v1.0\n
        Tired of hundreds of apps designed for humans to plan their trips,
        while your colony has to rely on toilet paper for notes?\n
        No more! Alcantarilla Trips is the first travel app designed exclusively
        for rodents. Plan your underground expeditions through the most popular sewers,
        discover new cheese routes and never get lost with your litter again.\n
        🧀 FEATURES\n
        - Itinerary Planning - Organize your trips and visualize your routes in seconds. 📅\n
        - Nearby Places Search - Find dumpsters, kitchens and more. 🧀\n
        - Image Storage - Save memories from your trips.\n
        - Advanced risk filters - Evaluate risk of grumpy humans in the area. 💀\n
        - Customize user preferences ⚙️\n
        - Multi-language support 🌎\n
        👥 TEAM\n
        - Àlex Escofet Presedo\n
        - Samuel Gomà Atehortua\n
        📍 VERSION\n
        Alcantarilla Trips 1.0.0\n
        This program uses \"THE BEER-WARE LICENSE\" (Revision 43)
    </string>
