    4. MODIFICATIONS\n
    Alcantarilla Trips reserves the right to modify these conditions at any time.
    Changes will be communicated through scratches on the walls of the main tunnel.\n\n

    5. ACCEPTANCE\n
    The mere act of sniffing this screen implies full acceptance of these terms.\n\n
